load ../provenance-completeness.maude

--- Coverage: a staged bundle assembles into the prompt WITH its evidence row present.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-PROVENANCE-COMPLETENESS :
  staged
  =>* assembled evidence .

--- Coverage: provenance is recorded (durable evidence row) before assembly.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-PROVENANCE-COMPLETENESS :
  staged
  =>* recorded evidence .

--- Bite: a bundle with no provenance source never reaches the prompt. The RESIDUAL
--- soup var means an assembled in ANY reachable state is a solution, so No solution
--- proves assembly is provenance-gated.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-PROVENANCE-COMPLETENESS :
  untracked
  =>* assembled RESIDUAL:Cfg .
